HEADWORD: Unfriendship
<hw>Un*friend"ship</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state or quality of
being unfriendly; unfriendliness; enmity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>An act of <qex>unfriendship</qex> to my sovereign person.</q>
